,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"742c8c22fa2223757340800a6a9856402a2ccbae","tid":577833,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0a7a4289f6f456ef4edc1f1896685df4f18a5232","tid":577833,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T06:07:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1382316-20180224.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1382316-20180224.htm&d=qSmWafg3Li5Pskn3cKC8XAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=939b6909\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1382316-20180224.htm&h=8002fb44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1382316-20180224.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n政府下星期三公布新一份財政預算案，立法會議員朱凱廸在一個電台節目說，現時社會太集中在應否「派錢」及金額水平，忽略了收入，擔心市民會有印象認為「賣地收入高是好事」，強調政府的賣地收入增加，樓價亦會居高不下。他認為，政府現時應考慮如何善用土地資源，建造更多市民可負擔的房屋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/164126/-%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E8%A3%9C%E9%81%B8-%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E8%B2%A1%E7%88%BA%E7%84%A1%E6%B4%BE%E9%8C%A2-%E5%80%A1%E7%8B%97%E5%B9%B4%E6%B4%BE9000-%E5%A8%A5%E5%A7%90-%E6%94%9D%E4%B8%80%E6%94%9D%E5%A4%AA%E6%AD%B2%E5%95%A6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F164126%2F-%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25A3%259C%25E9%2581%25B8-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%2588%25BA%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E9%258C%25A2-%25E5%2580%25A1%25E7%258B%2597%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%25B4%25BE9000-%25E5%25A8%25A5%25E5%25A7%2590-%25E6%2594%259D%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%2594%259D%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%2595%25A6&d=qSmWafg3Li5Pskn3cKC8XAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=3d6ee26d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/164126/-%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E8%A3%9C%E9%81%B8-%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E8%B2%A1%E7%88%BA%E7%84%A1%E6%B4%BE%E9%8C%A2-%E5%80%A1%E7%8B%97%E5%B9%B4%E6%B4%BE9000-%E5%A8%A5%E5%A7%90-%E6%94%9D%E4%B8%80%E6%94%9D%E5%A4%AA%E6%AD%B2%E5%95%A6</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180224/s00001/1519435769690\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180224%2Fs00001%2F1519435769690&d=qSmWafg3Li5Pskn3cKC8XAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=30aa6f36\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180224%2Fs00001%2F1519435769690&h=54bc3b9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180224/s00001/1519435769690</a><br />\n<br />\n梁耀忠今早在商台節目表示，以往街工的原則是不贊成派錢，但早前經調查，發現七成受訪者指政府亂花錢、理財不善，贊成派錢，所以他認為不如把錢派給市民，可以紓緩市民壓力。<br />\n<br />\n同場的張超雄表明不贊成派錢，認為派錢證明政府束手無策和無承擔。他說，政府的整體公共開支偏低，只佔國民生產總值不足兩成。他指日本、英國和歐洲等地的整體公共開支所佔比重遠比香港高。<br />\n<br />\n陳志全在節目上表示贊成派錢，認為「既然政府不肯做，不如還富於民」，又指退稅措施只是「還富於富」。他表示，派錢和將盈餘撥在其他方面，並非二擇其一。<br />\n<br />\n朱凱廸因感冒未能出席節目，陳志全則指朱在原則上不支持派錢，但更反對退稅，如果要選擇一個做法的話就寧願派錢。朱凱廸其後透過電話表示，現時的討論比較集中派錢，忽略了收入方面的討論，他擔心市民會有「賣地收入高是好事」的印象，日後樓價將會居高不下，變相亦是負擔，即使派錢，「日後供樓的錢都喺返度」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180220/20309655\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180220%2F20309655&d=qSmWafg3Li5Pskn3cKC8XAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=db08cf20\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180220%2F20309655&h=9e827e0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180220/20309655</a><br />\n<br />\n公民黨立法會議員郭家麒則表示，按照歐美國家的做法，應該只有在經濟衰退的時候才會選擇「派錢」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1145081/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1145081%2F&d=qSmWafg3Li5Pskn3cKC8XAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=ee617724\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1145081%2F&h=1f3a3861\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1145081/</a><br />\n<br />\n郭榮鏗梁繼昌反對派錢 邵家臻反對全民派<br />\n<br />\n屆政府首份財政預算案將於下星期發表，專業議政4名議員對政府在庫房大量盈餘下是否派錢意見不一。<br />\n<br />\n法律界郭榮鏗及會計界梁繼昌都反對派錢，認為是短視做法，行政費用高，負責任政府應該有願景，將盈餘用得其所用在醫療、教育及福利等方面。<br />\n<br />\n教育界葉建源就希望，BCA、即改革後的TSA農曆新年有好消息。認為如果政府做好長遠規劃，各種政策都得到社會支持後，直接派錢是可行的方法。<br />\n<br />\n社會福利界邵家臻建議，向65歲以上長者，每月直接派發3500元，及將盈餘投放在民間社會發展基金及關愛基金作融資安排，更較一次過派錢有效。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2015015/%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E6%B3%9B%E6%B0%91%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88%E6%B4%BE%E9%8C%A2%E3%80%80%E8%A7%92%E8%89%B2%E8%AA%BF%E6%8F%9B%EF%BC%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2015015%2F%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2588%25B6%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E6%25B3%259B%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%25AE%2597%25E6%25A1%2588%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E9%258C%25A2%25E3%2580%2580%25E8%25A7%2592%25E8%2589%25B2%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%258F%259B%25EF%25BC%259F&d=qSmWafg3Li5Pskn3cKC8XAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=dd4f9550\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2015015/%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E6%B3%9B%E6%B0%91%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88%E6%B4%BE%E9%8C%A2%E3%80%80%E8%A7%92%E8%89%B2%E8%AA%BF%E6%8F%9B%EF%BC%9F</a><br />\n<br />\n建制支持泛民反對預算案派錢　角色調換？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T06:08:01.000Z","msg":"樓主答我喇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T07:26:45.000Z","msg":"我屌泛民點解唔啱呀"},{"pid":"4a8ebd3718420789d0031b1b15aa71b2045ee9d8","tid":577833,"uid":24284,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T07:30:17.000Z","msg":"販民唔係保皇黨？<br />\n<br />\n12年政制係咩？<br />\n賦予小組主席大會主席嘅權力又係咩？<br />\n譴責拉布又係咩？<br />\n<br />\n以上全部都係保皇黨之所為，<br />\n點解我唔屌得，相反正正佢地以民主之名做有違民主之事，我先大大力屌"},{"pid":"8d36904b023b53346e0764877acf19838b8c6cbc","tid":577833,"uid":8858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T07:33:58.000Z","msg":"兩派共侍一主不用分這麼細<br />\n話時話民主回歸論肯認失敗未<br />\n屎總永續喎，真普選已經消失咗仲有面做反對派?"},{"pid":"74b2796f59dcc0dd37cb7ddf1a826523d136c00e","tid":577833,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:19:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"205abfc876349a8ff6c1ed9a10b633cabc955348","tid":577833,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T10:16:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f250798aecd9e1757a103fd6e83e5faf7ed301","tid":577833,"uid":173233,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T10:20:21.000Z","msg":"好明顯有班五毛專係射曬個波比泛民<br />\n之後睇下邊個得益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33207c2b120ab0d3cc8045227f058a2e4abdf3ee","tid":577833,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00f250798aecd9e1757a103fd6e83e5faf7ed301","tid":577833,"uid":173233,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T10:20:21.000Z","msg":"好明顯有班五毛專係射曬個波比泛民<br />\n之後睇下邊個得益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T10:23:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛dewibbg都撐泛民<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/03/182337_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F03%2F182337_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=5dcf0ec6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</span>"}]}